1. Google VRP – Up to $250k for Chrome/Android vulns. $64M+ total payouts.
2. Microsoft Bounty – $20k–$250k for Azure/Office 365.
3. Facebook/Meta Whitehat – $500–$100k.
4. HackerOne – 1,000+ programs (Uber, Shopify, Verizon Media).
5. Bugcrowd – 500+ programs (Atlassian $10k+).
6. Intigriti – EU-focused. $1k–$50k.
7. HackenProof – Web3/crypto payouts up to $100k.
⸻
5. Beginner’s Roadmap: Your First Bounty Hunt
1. Set up your lab – Install Docker, DVWA, Juice Shop, Burp Suite.
2. Learn the OWASP Top 10 – Practice each vuln in a sandbox.
3. Join beginner-friendly programs – Look for low-severity issues first.
4. Write clear, professional reports – Include reproduction steps.
5. Track your progress – Use a bounty journal to log lessons learned.
6. Expand into advanced scopes – APIs, mobile apps, and cloud platforms.
⸻
6. Additional Career Growth Strategies
• Join invite-only programs by maintaining consistent report quality.
• Focus on Web3 and crypto programs — payouts often run 2x higher.
• Build visibility with write-ups on Medium/X (e.g., NahamSec’s 2025 guide).
• Collaborate with peers on HackerOne/Intigriti for team invites.
• Engage in community challenges (CTFs, security conferences).
